<refsect1>
<title>Using BTK+ on Mac OS X</title>

<para>
The Mac OS X port of BTK+ is an implementation of BDK (and therefore BTK+) 
on top of the Quarz API.
</para>

<para>
Currently, the Mac OS X port does not use any additional commandline options
or environment variables. 
</para>

<para>
For up-to-date information about the current status of this port, see the
<ulink url="http://live.gnome.org/BTK+/OSX">project page</ulink>.
</para>

</refsect1>

